tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE trade_execution_optimization (
    trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    trade_type VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    trade_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    trade_symbol VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    trade_price DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
    trade_volume INT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE Trades (
    trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    trade_date DATE,
    symbol VARCHAR(50),
    trade_quantity INT,
    executed_price DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE Orders (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    order_date DATE,
    symbol VARCHAR(50),
    order_quantity INT,
    order_type VARCHAR(10),
    order_status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE trade_orders (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    symbol VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    quantity INT NOT NULL,
    price DOUBLE NOT NULL,
    executed BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE
);

CREATE TABLE trades ( trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	trade_symbol VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
	trade_quantity INT NOT NULL,
	trade_price DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
	trade_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
	INDEX symbol_idx (trade_symbol),
	INDEX quantity_idx (trade_quantity),
	INDEX price_idx (trade_price),
	INDEX timestamp_idx (trade_timestamp)
)

CREATE TABLE traders ( trader_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	trader_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
	trader_email VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
	trader_phone VARCHAR(15) NOT NULL,
	trader_address VARCHAR(255) NOT_NULL,
	INDEX name_idx (trader_name),
	INDEX email_idx (trader_email),
	INDEX phone_idx (trader_phone)
)

CREATE TABLE orders ( order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	trade_id INT NOT NULL,
	side ENUM('BUY', 'SELL') NOT NULL,
	order_quantity INT NOT NULL,
	order_price DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
	order_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
	INDEX trade_idx (trade_id),
	INDEX side_idx (side),
	INDEX quantity_idx (order_quantity),
	INDEX price_idx (order_price),
	INDEX timestamp_idx (order_timestamp)
)

CREATE TABLE executions ( execution_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	order_id INT NOT NULL,
	execution_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
	execution_price DECIMAL(10,2),
	execution_quantity INT NOT NULL,
	INDEX order_idx (order_id),
	INDEX timestamp_idx (execution_timestamp),
	INDEX price_idx (execution_price),
	INDEX quantity_idx (execution_quantity)
)

CREATE TABLE trades (
    trade_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    symbol VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    trade_volume INT NOT NULL,
    trade_price DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
    execution_time TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    trade_id INT NOT NULL,
    order_type VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,
    order_price DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
    order_status VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    first_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    last_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE executions (
    execution_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    trade_id INT NOT NULL,
    execution_type VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
    execution_time TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    execution_status VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL
);
